      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="student_view_for_multiple_answers_feedback" data-step-uuid="1C0F3D3A-8FB5-4AE5-9D33-9210227358EA">
    <h2 id="student_view_for_multiple_answers_feedback" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Student View for Multiple Answers Feedback</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/000/761/780/original/fda73dc1-4de1-44a1-a7c8-ca91135fb09c.png" srcset="" alt="Student View for Multiple Answers Feedback" height="512" width="712">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_5F818BD0-2229-0135-4A14-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>If you allow students to see the correct answers, correct responses are marked with a green flag [1]. Incorrect responses will be marked with a red flag [2] and any correct answers not indicated by the student are marked with a gray flag [3].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
